Unused method argument - `tolerated_status`. If it's necessary, use `_` or `_tolerated_status` as an argument name to indicate that it won't be used. You can also write as `test_tolerate_status(*)` if you want the method to accept any arguments but don't care about them. (https://github.com/bbatsov/ruby-style-guide#underscore-unused-vars)
